adutha &lt;unk&gt; ( tamil : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1983 tamil indian feature film directed by s. a. chandrasekhar . the film stars rajinikanth , lakshmi and radha in the lead roles . the music was composed by ilaiyaraaja and the lyrics were written by sujatha . the film was a super hit at the box office .